# PR 6 fixture: raw triple-quoted string literals.
# Backslash is literal (no escape processing); closing run must
# match the opening length.  Shorter `"` runs inside the body are
# literal content (the embedded-quote case exercises this).
# ASCII-only -- UTF-8 multi-byte emission for hex escapes is PR 7.
"""hello"""
"""back\nslash"""
"""line1
line2"""
"""""hi"""""
"""one"two""three"""
